  "title": "Solution Sales Manager - CyberSecurity",
  "description": "<p>We are partnering with a leading telecom client to hire a Solution Sales Manager (Cybersecurity) to drive revenue growth through solution-led, consultative selling. This role focuses on building strong customer relationships, developing opportunities, and closing complex cybersecurity deals across enterprise and public sector customers.</p><p>Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Drive cybersecurity solution sales by building and managing a strong pipeline across existing and new accounts</li><li>Partner closely with internal specialists and technical teams to develop outcome-based solutions aligned to customer needs</li><li>Engage customers to understand business challenges and position cybersecurity offerings as value-driven solutions</li><li>Own the end-to-end sales cycle from lead qualification through deal closure</li><li>Lead customer discussions, presentations, and negotiations, including engagement with senior and C-level stakeholders</li><li>Support bid and proposal processes by shaping commercial value propositions and managing deal risks</li><li>Collaborate with internal teams and external partners to deliver integrated solutions</li><li>Maintain accurate sales forecasts, pipeline reporting, and billing visibility</li><li>Ensure high levels of customer satisfaction across all engagements</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in IT, Business, Computer Science, or a related field</li><li>3–5 years of experience in solution sales, enterprise sales, or account management within IT / Telecommunications</li><li>Strong understanding of cybersecurity solutions and services</li><li>Experience selling solutions such as SIEM, IAM, SASE, network security, or managed security services</li><li>Exposure to government or public sector sales is an advantage</li><li>Strong commercial acumen with proven negotiation and closing skills</li><li>Excellent communication and stakeholder management skills</li><li>Self-motivated, results-driven, and comfortable working in a fast-paced environment</li></ul>",
